  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to study the management of the sprained ankle by help of
      NSAID-plaster. A questionnaire. The effect of RICE and RICE + NSAID-plaster in the treatment
      of the sprained ankle, compared by pain-score.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
